CY: # CY: Calendar year to which the week belongs. At the turn of the year
# Week: Calendar week according to DIN / ISO
# Ending: last day of the week (Sunday)
# NumberOfDeaths: Number of deaths in Switzerland of persons resident in Switzerland

# Expected: Number of deaths normally expected in this calendar week on the basis of previous years. Note: At each turn of the year there is a methodological break in the time series of expected values
# lowerB: lower limit of the 95% confidence interval of the expected value
# upperB: upper limit of the 95% confidence interval of the expected value
# Excess: In weeks where the number of deaths exceeds the upper limit of the expected value
